        <div class="portfolio-desc">
            <p>Liquid Light, in collaboration with <a href="https://yeseul.com">Yeseul Song</a>, is an interactive toy designed to simulate fluid dynamics with light. This piece explores how technology can refocus our attention back to the laws of nature that surround us and remind us of the playful nature of technology. Our project serves as a prototype for a toy in which multiple components of light can interact with one another (e.g. pouring light from one box to another).</p>
            <p>Special thanks to Danny Rozin.</p>
            <p>Liquid Light was showcased at the NYU ITP Winter Show in 2017.</p>
